185.5, 961.4, 835.5, 982.2]}, {"text": "$139", "bbox": [882.3, 961.4, 924.0, 982.2]}, {"text": "(3)", "bbox": [143.8, 1012.7, 168.1, 1033.6]}, {"text": "The acquired debt reflects capital lease obligations.", "bbox": [185.5, 1012.7, 614.0, 1033.6]}, {"text": "(4)", "bbox": [143.8, 1037.8, 168.1, 1058.6]}, {"text": "All of the goodwill was assigned to our general rentals segment. The level of goodwill that resulted from the", "bbox": [185.5, 1037.8, 1094.1, 1058.6]}, {"text": "acquisition is primarily reflective of NES’s going-concern value, the value of NES’s assembled workforce,", "bbox": [185.5, 1062.8, 1094.1, 1083.6]}, {"text": "new customer relationships expected to arise from the acquisition, and operational synergies that we expect", "bbox": [185.5, 1087.8, 1094.1, 1108.6]}, {"text": "to achieve that are not associated with the identifiable assets. $1 of goodwill is expected to be deductible for", "bbox": [185.5, 1112.8, 1094.1, 1133.6]}, {"text": "income tax purposes.", "bbox": [185.5, 1137.8, 362.2, 1158.6]}, {"text": "The years ended December 31, 2018 and 2017 include NES acquisition-related costs which are included in", "bbox": [185.5, 1189.2, 1094.2, 1210.0]}, {"text": "“Merger related costs” in our consolidated statements of income. The merger related costs are comprised of", "bbox": [143.8, 1214.2, 1094.2, 1235.0]}, {"text": "financial and legal advisory fees. In addition to the acquisition-related costs reflected in our consolidated", "bbox": [143.8, 1239.2, 1094.0, 1260.0]}, {"text": "statements of income, the debt issuance costs and the original issue premiums associated with the issuance of", "bbox": [143.8, 1264.2, 1094.2, 1285.0]}, {"text": "debt to fund the acquisition are reflected, net of amortization subsequent to the acquisition date, in long-term debt", "bbox": [143.8, 1289.2, 1094.1, 1310.0]}, {"text": "in our consolidated balance sheets.", "bbox": [143.8, 1314.2, 434.2, 1335.0]}, {"text": "Since the acquisition date, significant amounts of fleet have been moved between URI locations and the", "bbox": [185.5, 1365.6, 1094.1, 1386.4]}, {"text": "acquired NES locations, and it is not practicable to reasonably estimate the amounts of revenue and earnings of", "bbox": [143.8, 1390.6, 1094.2, 1411.4]}, {"text": "NES since the acquisition date. The impact of the NES acquisition on our equipment rentals revenue is primarily", "bbox": [143.8, 1415.6, 1093.9, 1436.4]}, {"text": "74", "bbox": [608.6, 1465.8, 629.4, 1486.6]}]}